                        <interp inst="t18360613-1443-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 20.—
<rs id="t18360613-1443-punishment-59" type="punishmentDescription">
